data.description:
Nestled in the charming community of Visalia, this spacious home offers a generous 2,151 square feet of living space, providing ample room for comfortable living. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, it caters to both family life and entertaining guests. The interior features a thoughtful combination of laminate flooring and carpet, creating a blend of warmth and practicality.
Situated on a 6,965-square-foot lot, the property offers a balance of indoor and outdoor space. The exterior showcases a stylish mix of stucco and stone, creating an eye-catching facade. The durable tile roof not only adds to the home's aesthetic appeal but also ensures long-lasting quality. This residence is not just a house; it's a well-designed and thoughtfully crafted home in the heart of Visalia, offering both comfort and style for those looking to make lasting memories in a welcoming community.
